messages.message: Any chance we could use paid commercial/community plans by default so there’s no time limit or are there live tests that rely on the plan being a trial?
i assume it must be difficult to create paid commercial/community plans programmatically for each PR’s CI?
Yea, harder to do and I didn’t want to create orgs with paid plans with weak passwords since we don’t have a good way to clean them up right now
Which stripe key is used on cypress crafting? Technically those plans could still be exploited if someone creates a paid plan using the dummy credit card (the Visa `4242…` )
Yep, that's true. I'd assume we are using the testing key.
